      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The engine struggles to start and requires immediate mechanical attention, while the transmission exhibits significant slipping. Visually, the body has several areas of rust, major dents, and peeling paint, and the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is not currently roadworthy and will need to be towed.",
